Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.57,0:00:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.05,0:00:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.65,0:00:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撲克光線BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.69,0:00:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.46,0:00:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.66,0:00:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.07,0:00:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.44,0:00:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.21,0:00:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.75,0:00:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.35,0:01:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢想與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.79,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧，BRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.60,0:01:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(佛特的遺跡燉煮麻煩醬菜)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種地方會有遺跡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就是為了\N調查這個而來的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得好恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.60,0:01:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，這裡好像墳場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.14,0:01:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個在怕什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.24,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾千年前這個星球早已滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.75,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有生物的話\N也只有我們而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.69,0:02:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...那再挖下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會\N有鬼之類的東西出現吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冤枉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.96,0:02:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要嚇我啦！佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.97,0:02:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木乃伊也好，吸血鬼也好\N都出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會比這無聊的挖掘工作\N還要有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人真是夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說了什麼呀？諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在正站在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.58,0:02:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記錄了數千年歷史的\N偉大遺跡前耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣虔敬的心情或是浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們一點都沒有感覺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.66,0:02:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法式糖炒栗子的話\N我蠻會做的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然和這種無知、無教養\N無神經的人一起出來是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.94,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是香草的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會同意我的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，若能跟香草一起來該有多好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳想做什麼？佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危險耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼討厭我們的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.95,0:03:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾脆把你綁在飛彈上\N送回香草所在的基地好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用麻煩了，謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.56,0:03:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那以後你說話要注意一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦，我們快點完成任務吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像又找到什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.84,0:03:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然，妳的好運異於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是\N好像跟遺跡沒多大關係耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是蛋耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？怎麼敲不破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳想吃掉它嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不是想要吃掉它嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是變成化石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老鼠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特妳看，好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪...哪裡可愛了啊？這種小老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.84,0:04:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，這傢伙在瞪我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在說什麼啊，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是剛剛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是妳搞錯了\N對不對？小可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.52,0:04:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看，牠這麼可愛\N怎麼會瞪人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.05,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還很黏人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要不要抱抱看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:05:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要...今天不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不必客氣啊，來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是跟妳說過我不要的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特妳怎麼了？流好多汗耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.08,0:05:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼可以這樣子，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特妳原來...真令人意外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人真的是不可貌相啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.74,0:05:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連哭泣的小孩\N看到都會安靜的佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然也有害怕的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.98,0:05:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且怕的還是小老鼠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.78,0:05:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特妳怕牠嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼可愛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把這小老鼠丟掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.83,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫牠取名叫  「小太」  吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣，喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還呵呵咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把牠丟掉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特妳去把牠丟掉不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來事情就簡單多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛...還是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非妳不敢摸老鼠嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀！這件事\N要是讓天使隊的人知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.86,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說，大家一定笑破肚皮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去有笑話可以跟大家說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德，你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是妳希望我，不要告訴大家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是和我談條件嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.97,0:06:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果妳答應我不傷害小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會跟大家說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.78,0:07:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有\N以後妳不能再稱呼我"這傢伙"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了\N太好了，小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了！我抓到佛特的弱點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來可以過一陣好日子了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.14,0:07:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特\N要不要過來這邊吃飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有熱湯可喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了，我沒食慾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真稀奇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特竟然也會沒食慾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...要繼續去找遺跡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過敏雖然是退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，我竟被那兩個人瞧不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都是那隻臭老鼠的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，好癢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙也在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要在那邊鬼鬼崇崇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.06,0:08:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要親手殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來吧！小老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然敢耍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就讓你見識見識\N我真的生氣時是什麼樣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你不是普通的老鼠吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太，小太你在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，小太你在這裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特有沒有欺負你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離這傢伙遠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要叫牠"這傢伙"了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠的名字叫作"小太"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼小太呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳給我聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙，嘴巴會吐出光線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一瞬間就把這火箭砲\N開了個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.36,0:09:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是披了老鼠皮的怪物呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會是怪物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.37,0:09:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是佛特說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才害小太嚇跑了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙怎麼可能被嚇跑嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太牠...小太牠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變這麼大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.79,0:10:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼可愛的小太竟然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正所謂小時了了\N大未必佳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這個問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.41,0:10:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是破壞幕斯卡文明的生物武器\NBIOTECH  WEAPON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太是武器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼可以\N把這麼重要的事給忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健忘癥嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人都會有的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健忘癥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙還算是電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.03,0:10:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙果然是怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可怕的瘟神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.83,0:10:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論牠變得多大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太還是小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是笨蛋嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠可是生物武器呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠在太空中也能生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許會去其他星球\N鬧得天翻地覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑\N這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.16,0:11:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是妳把蛋弄破的\N妳要想辦法解決喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.14,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想到一個好方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.18,0:11:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就叫作廢物利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你利用了老鼠的本能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.79,0:11:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管牠的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.82,0:11:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概會轉一輩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太看起來好開心的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(下個菜單是\N遊樂園名產，雞肉薄荷蜜餞)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.17,0:11:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花．法蘭波瓦茲\N與佛特．修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.80,0:11:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人在那天衝進了槍林彈雨中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.34,0:11:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人就再也沒有回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.64,0:12:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我新月的曲線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.48,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做了夢之後，變得想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,側耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.75,0:12:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是聽見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.29,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人興奮的天線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.27,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓它睡著  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.38,0:13:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向巨蟹座的你發出\N急電，急電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.41,0:13:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著飛馬的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DARLING  LOVING  YOU

